com.salesforce.androidsdk.smartsync.manager

Class MetadataSyncManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.salesforce.androidsdk.smartsync.manager.MetadataSyncManager

  • public class MetadataSyncManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides an easy way to fetch metadata using MetadataSyncDownTarget. This class handles creating a soup, storing synched data and reading it into a meaningful data structure, i.e. Metadata.
    Author:
    bhariharan
